<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,1485,2031]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,311,1485,1511]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Distribution.</emphasis>
Saharo-Sindian species, distributed from 
<collectingCountry box="[801,907,1485,1511]" name="Morocco" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Morocco</collectingCountry>
to 
<collectingCountry box="[944,1014,1485,1511]" name="Egypt" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Egypt</collectingCountry>
